thoughts: Interesting and fun, but pay was much too low to continue. So I stopped.

For the first round, I wasn't sure if I was supposed to answer the questions based on how I think the person would be feeling in that situation or based off the information given in the story alone. I answered most of the questions in that round based only on the information given, but started to guess how they would feel since no information was given about how the person was feeling.
I'd like to continue with the study but was unable to allocate more time. I made it 50 rounds. Please feel free to contact me if you'd like more participation.
I hope you find my participation to be somewhat helpful and beneficial to your research.
